Mobile application to simplify stock management and inventory control, through barcode reading.

// AGILE INVENTORY MANAGEMENT PROCESS
Records by reading barcodes through the device camera or scanner, when applicable, with association of the respective amount.

// ACCURACY IN INVENTORY CONTROL
Option for reading only the existing products in database, with the possibility of validation of the amount value.

// SIMPLICITY IN TAX OBLIGATIONS
With direct integration to ETPOS customers, this application uses the XML format defined by tributary and customs Portuguese authority, with fiscal number association, in order to facilitate compliance with the inventory reporting requirement.

// INCREASE PRODUCTIVITY
Export records in CSV and XML formats.
